H> l wol
You see Wolfbane Crag, a striking male wolfling with broad well-developed
shoulders. His image seems to be shrouded by a mysterious mist causing him
to shimmer before you. His eyes are like bottomless deep hazel pools.
He is wearing a silvered steel helm set with two curving ivory horns, some
blackened deeplander armor emblazoned with the flying eagle of the Crimson Band
upon the chest, a ruby studded silver ring of the Crimson Band, a black
shimmering cloak emblazoned with a griffin clutched in the talons of a white
dragon in flight, some sooty black leather gloves, a golden emerald studded
scabbard embossed with "Brave Defender of Fayd", some sooty black leather boots
and a hard leather satchel with an exquisite hand painted scene of a healer
tending a warrior's wounds.
He is wielding an icy randar papenheimer and an ice encrusted albescent
longsword with a crossguard of elkyri and a pommel formed like a screaming
eagle.
He radiates with magical strength.
He is outlined in glowing armor.
He is protected by a ghostly, hovering shield.
He appears to be healthy.
He has a nicked and grazed head and a singed right arm.
