You see Delight D'Marcan, and she is delightful! Sunkissed auburn hair tumbles
in loose curls around her bronzed shoulders. The light in her dancing brown
eyes sparks mischievously whenever she smiles.
She is wearing some blackened eldritch titanium armor inset with an onyx stone
in the shape of a black wingless dragon, some deeplander boots, a delicate ring
made entirely of interwoven thorns, a blackened steel helm delicately inlaid
with rows of onyx stones, a soft black wristlet adorned with a delicate gold
chain that runs through two sturdy metal loops, a coral hairpin, a sheer black
spidersilk gown traced with silver webbing and clasped with a solid silver
spider at her bosom and some fingerless black leather gloves with an unusual
symbol on them: infinity gripped at its center by a hand.
She is wielding a snow-white diamontine shield etched with a black, wingless
dragon staring raptly at a dove that flies above.
She looks pale and worn.
She has a nicked head, a nicked body, a nicked back, a lacerated right arm, a
lacerated left arm, a nicked left leg and a grazed right hand.
DEAD> 
Delight is now following Wolfbane.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes down.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, valley]
Several large boulders are strewn about the valley floor here, no doubt having
rolled from the fractured peaks of the mountains above. Two particularly
massive boulders have come to rest in midstream, channelling the flow of water
between them into a roaring, frothing chute.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: north, south.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes south.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, valley]
Two great mountain peaks flank the valley on either side here, like the towers
of a titanic gatehouse. At their very peak, a cap of snow remains intact from
the winter, and rivulets of water from the snowy cap course down the slopes to
join the waters of the stream. The enormity of the mountains makes the wide
valley seem tight and claustrophic despite its considerable width. Occasional
uquart trees dot the few flat spots along their steep slopes.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: north, southwest.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes southwest.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, valley]
A slight turn in the stream's course has created a beach of polished stones on
this bank of the stream. On the opposite side, an undercut rock face hangs
ominously over the stream, threatening to drop at any moment. Several large
rocks in midstream are evidence that the stream has been cutting into the
cliff for some time. A number of tiny swallows dart in and out of holes
bored into the softer soil of the cliff, bringing food for their young.
From all the way on the other side of the stream, you can clearly hear
the cries of hungry chicks screaming for a bit of nourishment.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: northeast, southwest.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes southwest.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, streambed]
A sheet of spray splashes over a worn outcrop of terraced bedrock here, hissing
like a gentle shower. Amidst the curtains of mist, a delicate clump of white
penetine blossoms cling to a mossy ledge. The path and the stream meander down
through the mountains to the south, and rise towards a great gap in the massive
peaks to the northeast.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. Some white penetine blossoms are here.
Obvious exits: south, northeast.
DEAD> 
Delight exclaims, "Wait!"
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes south.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, streambed]
A frothing mountain stream surges down the mountains, rolling over the mossy
rocks and debris in its bed with reckless abandon. Downstream from here, the
massive rock walls of the valley close tightly around the stream. To the north,
however, the valley widens somewhat. Countless eons of traffic by all sorts of
travellers have worn a fine trail which winds northward through the the valley
towards towering mountain peaks. Another path of loose rubble leads up the
steep valley wall.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: north, up.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes up.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, scramble]
Bits of broken rock and other rubble from a recent slide have made something of
a path here, allowing careful travellers access to a lush but rugged valley
which cuts through the mountain range. Here and there, delicate white flowers
poke up through the gaps in the rubble. The rocks are quite unstable, though,
and each step must be made with great care to avoid disaster.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: up, down.
DEAD> 
Delight concentrates intently.
Delight erects a wall of force around her body.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes up.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, rocky trail]
A wide section of the hillside has slumped downward here, cutting a pass
through the otherwise impassable mountain peaks. A number of trees dot the
mountainside, their leaves arching out in perfect minitures of the great trees
of the forests of the lowlands. Although they seem to be mature, or even old
trees, the winds and cold of the mountain has greatly stunted their growth . A
steep slope leads down towards a deep valley below.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: down.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane's group goes down a rocky trail.
DEAD> 
Wolfbane carries you.
[Teeth of Shartan, canyon view]
A recent rockslide has filled in a section of the slope below the widening
mountain path, piling a trail of rocks and debris against the cliff.  Far
below, the wavering silver line of a stream threads through a rugged mountain
canyon.  The fog continues to dissipate to the southeast.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: west, southeast.
