Fog blankets the entire area here, even obscuring the bridge somewhat. A ledge
runs around the mountain disappearing into the vapor. Interesting footprints
can be seen clearly in the dust below when you look down.
You see Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: northeast, southeast.
