Wolfbane's group goes through a door.
J> 
You follow Wolfbane.
[Sojourner's Hospice, entry way]
The Hospice is always open to adventurers for free, as Lirien the Inn Keeper
was once a warrior himself. He is always ready to trade a room for a tale of
adventure. Under an archway to the west is a flop. Odd colors, wafting smoke,
music and revelry come from a cantina to the east. A stairway leads to the
private rooms upstairs.
You see Madrina, Wolfbane and Delight. 
Obvious exits: east, west, out.
